The AmaXhosa bid farewell to their king Mpendulo Zwelonke Sigcawu in a ceremony that was a celebration of his life. Speaker after speaker tells of a man who used his voice to speak out against all forms of injustice. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - AmaXhosa bid farewell to their King Mpendulo Zwelonke Sigcawu in a ceremony that was a celebration of his life. King Sigcawu made a positive impact on his community who speak highly of him. READ: Ramaphosa hails amaXhosa King as a great leader Locals say they will honour his legacy by instilling the lessons taught to them by the king.